---
// About tab panel body: avatar + conversational bio (verbatim copy).
---

<div class="about">
  <img
    class="about__avatar"
    src="/avatar.jpg"
    width="112"
    height="112"
    alt="Stanley Tejakusuma avatar"
    loading="lazy"
    decoding="async"
  />
  <p class="section-copy">
    Hey hey! I'm Stanley. I live and breathe data working in between blockchain and analytics space.
    Started out as a data scientist and it turned into a habit I can't shake: whenever something has
    numbers behind it, I become curious to know what they're really saying. Markets, blockchains,
    models, you name it, even my own routines all look like datasets to me. I learn better by first
    understanding the full contextual insight, then take action upon it - sometimes breaking things
    along the way but it's part of the learning curve 😉.
  </p>
  <p class="section-copy">
    Most of my work sits where data meets real decision. I deep dive into on-chain activity and turn
    it into actionable insights, build and backtest systematic trading strategies, and fine-tuning
    language models to run on household hardware. The domain/subject may change, but chasing the
    signal in the noise never does.
  </p>
  <p class="section-copy">
    I rarely stop at the analysis. I build the pipelines that collect the data, the models that learn
    from it, and the tools that act upon it. I came up through data science and taught myself the
    rest by shipping things that had real consequences (fire drill *ugh). I care a ton about making
    complex systems simple enough to actually trust; whether a human or an agent is using them.
  </p>
  <p class="section-copy">
    Outside of work, you can see me in either a Tennis or Padel court. That, or, perhaps in the
    nearest mountain in the Java island. I'm always looking to make mine and people's life easier.
    Never stop grinding. Stay hungry and stay foolish.
  </p>
</div>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 66ch;
  }

  .about .section-copy {
    font-size: 0.94rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .about__avatar {
    float: left;
    width: clamp(72px, 8vw, 88px);
    height: auto;
    margin: 0.2rem 1.25rem 0.6rem 0;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .about .section-copy + .section-copy {
    margin-top: 0.85rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .about__avatar {
      float: none;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 0 1.1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
